"{\"uid\": \"timesnownews.com-india-olympic-star-vinesh-phogat-joins-farmers-protest-what-this-means-for-the-agitation-article-112941679\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"India  Vinesh Phogat joins protesting farmers at Shambhu border (File Photo)  New Delhi:Wrestler Vinesh Phogat on Saturday joined the protesting farmers at the Shambhu border on the 200th day of the agitation.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999988597785111, \"rank\": 6.695892418191744e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9682213451771684, \"rank\": 0.03282168378265718, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ace wrestler backed the farmers on their key demands and also urged the government to listen to their grievances.\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been 200 days since they are sitting here.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is painful to see this.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of them are citizens of this country.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Farmers run the country.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing is possible without them, not even athletes-if they do not feed us, we will not be able to compete,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat continued, \\\"Many a time we are helpless and can not do anything.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We represent the country at such big levels, but we can not do anything for our family even when we see them sad.\\\"\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I urge the Government that they should listen.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They had admitted their mistake last time; they should fulfill the promises that they made.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The country will not progress if people sit on the streets like this,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The protest which enters the 200th day today began on February 13, after authorities prevented their march to Delhi.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9999998114926889, \"rank\": 1.8850719423223123e-07, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The farmers have raised the issue of Minimum Support Price (MSP) for all crops, a demand which has not yet been met by the Centre.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1182, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_Scottish_Parliament\", \"score\": 0.7607185262690458, \"rank\": 0.31454639490988523, \"text\": \"MSP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_Scottish_Parliament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Member_of_the_Scottish_Parliament\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, farmers are also demanding decisive action against Bollywood actress and Member of Parliament (MP) Kangana Ranaut, urging the BJP to address her controversial remarks, which have previously provoked strong reactions from the farming community.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mumbai\", \"score\": 0.9313474281953161, \"rank\": 0.06954419994993641, \"text\": \"Bollywood\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mumbai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mumbai\"}, {\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.993985872284971e-14, \"text\": \"Parliament\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_India\"}, {\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kangana Ranaut\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\"}, {\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.483719742173904e-14, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kangana's remarks on the protest drew sharp responses from the farmers and the Opposition parties.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The BJP too has distanced itself from her remark.\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.483719742173904e-14, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BJP also directed the actor-turned-politician not to give such statements in future.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.483719742173904e-14, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whatever Kangana Ranaut has stated regarding the farmers' agitation, the party does not subscribe to her views,\\\" the BJP said.\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kangana Ranaut\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\"}, {\"begin\": 1867, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.483719742173904e-14, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The statement made by BJP MP Kangana Ranaut in the context of the farmers' movement is not the opinion of the party.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1901, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.483719742173904e-14, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kangana Ranaut\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Bharatiya Janata Party expresses its disagreement with the statement made by Kangana Ranaut,\\\" the party said in the statement.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 0.999999805916578, \"rank\": 1.9408352742926384e-07, \"text\": \"Bharatiya Janata Party\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kangana Ranaut\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversy erupted when Kangana Ranaut posted a video on her X handle, alleging that the farmers' protest could have led to anarchy in India similar to that in Bangladesh.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kangana Ranaut\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kangana_Ranaut\"}, {\"begin\": 2268, \"end\": 2273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999988597785111, \"rank\": 6.695892418191744e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 2293, \"end\": 2303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangladesh\", \"score\": 0.9999994115675602, \"rank\": 5.884328575757371e-07, \"text\": \"Bangladesh\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangladesh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangladesh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The actor-turned-politician claimed that external forces were conspiring to destabilize India with the aid of \\\"insiders.\\\"\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999988597785111, \"rank\": 6.695892418191744e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ranaut also alleged that during the farmers' protest against the now-repealed farm laws, there were instances of \\\"bodies hanging and rapes taking place.\\\"\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said that such violence was averted only due to the foresight of India's leadership.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2651, \"end\": 2656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999988597785111, \"rank\": 6.695892418191744e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The farmers are also expected to reveal their strategy for the upcoming Haryana elections in the near future.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2744, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.971074303435699e-17, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For theLatest news,India Newsand breaking stories from around theworld, visitTimes Nowfor live coverage and in-depth reporting.\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anurag Kumar is an Assistant Editor at Times Now, where he plays a